  <summary date="2018-04-10T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Correct the Census Count Act 

This bill requires the Department of Commerce, beginning with the 2020 decennial census, to attribute to an individual who is incarcerated in a correctional center as of the date on which such census is taken such individual's last place of residence before incarceration.</summary>
